\'a0 \'a0 \'a0or raw stack traces?\
\'a0 \'a0- **Denial of Service**: Are there rate limits on expensive database or LLM\
\'a0 \'a0 \'a0queries?\
\'a0 \'a0- **Elevation of Privilege**: Can an unauthenticated user bypass access\
\'a0 \'a0 \'a0control to reach privileged tool actions?\
